  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a single-institution, prospective, one-to-one randomized controlled research study.
      Subjects medically determined to need a cholecystectomy will be consented for surgery and
      study participation prior to enrolment in this study. Patients will then be randomized to
      receive either a single port laparoscopic cholecystectomy or a four port laparoscopic
      cholecystectomy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
